Revision history for URL::Check

0.11   Wed Mar 30 16:15:00 2016 MANWAR
       - Added test scripts (t/manifest.t, t/meta-json.t and t/meta-yml.t).
       - Added MANIFEST.SKIP file.
       - Updated copyright year information.

0.10   Wed Dec 16 10:50:00 2015 MANWAR
       - Updated Copyright year information.
